{"tid":1533131,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"五大訴求 已經outdate啦屌","createTime":"2019-09-02T16:19:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T17:56:00.000Z","uid":92182,"like":23,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e0fe018dfb62571a2a1c6f154316b2a973dd6c18","tid":1533131,"uid":92182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:19:30.000Z","msg":"我地一路講緊缺一不可嘅五大訴求，事到如今已經out撚曬date<br />\n<br />\n一路講緊：<br />\n一、全面撤回送中條例<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">二、成立獨立調查委員會</span><br />\n三、撤回暴動定性<br />\n四、釋放被捕義士<br />\n五、落實真普選<br />\n<br />\n想問下，成立獨立調查委員會有乜撚柒野用，諗都諗撚到，結果咪又係自己人查自己人，睇下鉛水單野盲嘅都見到啦屌<br />\n<br />\n唔該，以後講<span style=\"color: red;\"> 「解散警隊，清算黑警」</span><br />\n只有解散警隊，清算所有黑警先會為香港帶嚟出路<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"51f1f3e54a666f988830d6d218780779c19561e8","tid":1533131,"uid":92182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:19:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f9e28a77ddf271dec1e609de3f2c287a6d850d57","tid":1533131,"uid":93383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:20:19.000Z","msg":"Yes"},{"pid":"4798ed9994b0aa9f37eb0f2f3ef39fe44513633e","tid":1533131,"uid":92182,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:21:04.000Z","msg":"獨立調查委員會托柒嫁咋屌 係要解散警隊啊屌你老母"},{"pid":"e86cadbd7abc4beec2360042795244d07676c6f5","tid":1533131,"uid":92182,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:22:37.000Z","msg":"推 1/10"},{"pid":"fc9256feb2256a94cfbec8e9d96756751ad212b8","tid":1533131,"uid":92182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:22:51.000Z","msg":"推 2/10"},{"pid":"2f8777a63c5da88c1abf4349d6b24cf9af040938","tid":1533131,"uid":44323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:22:52.000Z","msg":"嗌香港獨立咪算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3812c17a7927fb91db22f517675a82e2170642f5","tid":1533131,"uid":92182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit